        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4139695324" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7216286603676865496">James Scott reverses the conventional historical narratives on the evolution of civilization by revealing the purposeful intention and maneuver deployed by hill people of the Zomia massif that escaping for freedom is a driver behind the changes of civilization lifestyles. <br/>Swidden agriculture is not necessarily backward than padi wet rice growing. It is more versatile and said to provide more nutrients of a variety of sources instead of carbonhydrates alone. <br/>Hill people, in their search for liber</span>
  <span id="freeText7216286603676865496" style="display:none">James Scott reverses the conventional historical narratives on the evolution of civilization by revealing the purposeful intention and maneuver deployed by hill people of the Zomia massif that escaping for freedom is a driver behind the changes of civilization lifestyles. <br />Swidden agriculture is not necessarily backward than padi wet rice growing. It is more versatile and said to provide more nutrients of a variety of sources instead of carbonhydrates alone. <br />Hill people, in their search for liberty and tax free labor free lifestyle, created a variety of devices and cultural arrangements to facilitate the versatility and agility of their movements. Planting yams and potatoes, not rice, helps them evade appropriation and taxation. Enforcing egalitarian hierarchy, far from what civilized valley people had denigrated them to be, is a cultural apparatus for fast movement and assemblage of social units during crises. Similarly, the lack of written system may also be purposefully designed to assist with agile movement and breakdown of rigid social structure by having no one remembers reified histories. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7216286603676865496" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


